---
title: Cheesy Leek Tart with Apple and Baby Leaf Salad
description: Spring has sprung! A new season of veg is ready for our plates, which is why we've created this Cheesy Leek Tart. Making the most of sweet leeks, this easy, creamy tart is sure to put a spring in your step.
